e\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation web\">Watson, George (22 November 1998). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/hitler-and-the-socialist-dream-1186455.html\">\"Hitler and the Socialist Dream\"</a>. Independent<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 July</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Hitler+and+the+Socialist+Dream&amp;rft.pub=Independent&amp;rft.date=1998-11-22&amp;rft.aulast=Watson&amp;rft.aufirst=George&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Farts-entertainment%2Fhitler-and-the-socialist-dream-1186455.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AV%C3%B6lkerabf%C3%A4lle\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-SS_16:37-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-SS_16:37_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">minute 16:37 Film \"The Soviet Story\"</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Dyukov-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Dyukov_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Alexander, Dyukov. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rugraz.net/index.php/ru/istoricheskoe-dostoinstvo/mifi-o-rossii-i-cccp/1009-alexander-dyukov-the-soviet-story-the-tissue-of-lies\">\"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">\"</span>THE SOVIET STORY\" \u2014 The tissue of lies\"</a>. <i>rugraz.netaz Net</i> (in Russian). Mag. Andrej W. Sidenko<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">27 July</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fm